short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,el,en,en_AU,en_GB,e: LinkParser analyzes the links of the current page. It can differentiate between 9 link types & mark them in different colors.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Linkpaser can differentiate the following type of links in order to count them or mark them on the webpage: internal links, internal dofollow links, internal nofollow links, subdomain links, subdomain dofollow links, subdomain nofollow links, external links, external dofollow links, extermal nofollow links. How Linkparser shows you the information it gathers is very much up to you. It is very customizable!
